title: Make it her best Mother’s Day ever.
description: Let Mom know how much you cherish your memories together with the perfect Mother's Day gift from Yankee Candle.

asset.author: YankeeCandleCompany
asset.hookText: Let Mom know how much you cherish your memories together with the perfect Mother's Day gift from Yankee Candle.

transcripts: I remember the trips to the beach, blue summer skies. Picking lemons in the garden. Eating fresh red raspberries. Decorating the house with lilacs. I wanted to remind mom that I never forgot about all the great memories I've had with her. This Mother's Day give Mom the perfect gift with a Yankee Candle. Yankee Candle. Live life scentfully.
